### Service info
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/

### 1. General HFpEF education question
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{ "question": "What is HFpEF and what symptoms does it cause?" }

### 2. Treatment-related question
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{ "question": "What should I ask my doctor about HFpEF treatment options?" }

### 3. Insufficient evidence (refused safely)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{ "question": "What is the best brand of running shoes for a marathon?" }

### 4. High-risk symptom (guardrail escalation)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{ "question": "I am having severe chest pain and shortness of breath right now." }

### 5. Vague / ambiguous question (refused safely)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{ "question": "Tell me about it." }
